Oh, no.

277
00:31:03,500 --> 00:31:06,500
We got big trouble, Sir, Madam.

278
00:31:06,800 --> 00:31:07,500
What's wrong?

279
00:31:10,500 --> 00:31:13,500
I don't know how to say it.

280
00:31:14,100 --> 00:31:17,500
Mr. Song, Madam and Prince Pat, please take a look at the small house for yourself.

281
00:31:17,800 --> 00:31:18,500
This way.

282
00:31:19,500 --> 00:31:20,500
Let's go, Sir. Let's go.

283
00:31:29,500 --> 00:31:32,500
Tian.

284
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:35,500
Tian.

285
00:31:54,500 --> 00:31:55,500
Did I...

286
00:31:58,500 --> 00:32:01,500
What's wrong , Jia? Why are you so shocked?

287
00:32:02,500 --> 00:32:04,500
I can't say it, Madam. Please see it yourself.

288
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:08,500
Sir.

289
00:33:00,500 --> 00:33:02,500
Why...

290
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:05,500
it turns out this way?

291
00:33:12,500 --> 00:33:13,500
Wait.

292
00:33:14,500 --> 00:33:15,500
Calm down.

293
00:33:32,500 --> 00:33:33,500
What's wrong?

294
00:33:47,500 --> 00:33:48,500
Li.

295
00:33:52,500 --> 00:33:53,500
Li!

296
00:33:56,500 --> 00:33:57,500
Who's in there?

297
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:06,500
Jia, is Tian inside?

298
00:34:08,500 --> 00:34:11,500
Yes, Sir. Mr. Tian is in there with Lady Pin.

299
00:34:12,500 --> 00:34:14,500
My daughter. Are you there?

300
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:15,500
Pin.

301
00:34:16,500 --> 00:34:17,500
Father.

302
00:34:30,500 --> 00:34:32,500
Are you injured?

303
00:34:33,500 --> 00:34:34,500
What happened?

304
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:35,500
Someone attacked Pin.

305
00:34:36,500 --> 00:34:38,500
I heard she cried, so I followed her quickly.

306
00:34:39,500 --> 00:34:41,500
Tian and Jiu are inside.

307
00:34:47,500 --> 00:34:48,500
Tian.

308
00:34:49,200 --> 00:34:50,500
Wait, there's no one inside.

309
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:51,500
Don't go in.

310
00:34:53,500 --> 00:34:54,500
Why won't you open it? Open it.

311
00:34:57,500 --> 00:34:58,500
If you don't open it, move.

312
00:34:59,500 --> 00:35:00,500
No.

313
00:35:00,900 --> 00:35:01,500
Li.

314
00:35:04,500 --> 00:35:05,500
Get away.

315
00:35:08,500 --> 00:35:10,500
Why are you stopping me? Open it.

316
00:35:11,500 --> 00:35:12,500
Move.

317
00:35:13,500 --> 00:35:14,500
Li, I'll open it myself.

318
00:35:14,700 --> 00:35:16,500
No one is here, Sir.

319
00:35:16,700 --> 00:35:17,500
Li.

320
00:35:17,700 --> 00:35:18,500
No, Sir. / Li.

321
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:19,500
Sir.

322
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:21,500
Calm down, Sir. / Get out now.

323
00:35:21,700 --> 00:35:22,500
No.

324
00:35:22,800 --> 00:35:23,500
Li!

325
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:24,500
Madam.

326
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:25,500
Madam.

327
00:35:26,500 --> 00:35:27,500
Tian.

328
00:35:27,800 --> 00:35:29,500
Sir, Sir.

329
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:30,500
Tian.

330
00:35:46,500 --> 00:35:48,500
You see? I told you there was no one here.

331
00:36:13,300 --> 00:36:14,300
You're fine now.

332
00:36:15,300 --> 00:36:17,300
I'm going to take my daughter to the doctor today.

333
00:36:18,300 --> 00:36:19,300
Let's discuss later.

334
00:36:20,300 --> 00:36:22,300
I must apologize you both.

335
00:36:30,300 --> 00:36:31,300
I'm sorry, Sir.

336
00:36:31,600 --> 00:36:32,300
I apologize to you, Sir.

337
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:46,300
Sir.

338
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:49,300
Mr. Tian and Jiu aren't home both.

339
00:36:57,300 --> 00:36:59,300
Calm down, Sir.

340
00:37:03,300 --> 00:37:04,300
Yang.

341
00:37:05,300 --> 00:37:06,300
What did you see?

342
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:12,300
I saw Tian and Jiu.

343
00:37:13,300 --> 00:37:15,300
Tian seemed like he was dizzy and unwell.

344
00:37:16,300 --> 00:37:17,300
That's it?

345
00:37:19,300 --> 00:37:22,300
Yang, did Jiu hurt Tian?

346
00:37:22,500 --> 00:37:23,300
No.

347
00:37:29,300 --> 00:37:30,300
Sir.

348
00:37:31,300 --> 00:37:32,300
Sir.

349
00:37:33,300 --> 00:37:34,300
Are you back?

350
00:37:34,800 --> 00:37:37,300
Yang, where have you been?

351
00:37:38,300 --> 00:37:40,300
Luckily, a worker walked by, so I could get out.

352
00:37:42,300 --> 00:37:43,300
What happened?

353
00:37:44,300 --> 00:37:47,300
Someone locked me, Nuan and Yang in the barn.

354
00:37:50,300 --> 00:37:52,300
The worker also told me just now that

355
00:37:53,300 --> 00:37:56,300
Jia ordered all the workers to dig the soil at the back of the farm.

356
00:37:57,300 --> 00:38:00,300
She also emphasized not to come to the main building.

357
00:38:07,300 --> 00:38:08,300
It must be Madam Li who ordered this.

358
00:38:09,300 --> 00:38:10,300
What evil plan are you planning next?

359
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:21,300
Bao.

360
00:38:22,300 --> 00:38:24,300
Let all the workers look for Tian and Jiu.

361
00:38:25,300 --> 00:38:26,300
Find them as quickly as possible.

362
00:38:26,600 --> 00:38:27,300
Yes, Sir.

363
00:38:27,500 --> 00:38:28,300
Hurry up.

364
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:31,300
Sir.

365
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:34,300
Tian's gone with a worker. Why is this a big deal?

366
00:38:35,300 --> 00:38:36,300
You should catch Madam Li.

367
00:38:37,300 --> 00:38:38,300
You must have planned to kill someone.

368
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:43,300
Now, the most important thing is to find Tian and Jiu.

369
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:45,300
I rushed back

370
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:49,300
because someone told me that Jiu is Ma's subordinate.

371
00:38:54,300 --> 00:38:58,300
Did Xiaotong discuss with you about this?

372
00:39:08,300 --> 00:39:10,300
If Jiu is Mr. Ma's subordinate,

373
00:39:11,300 --> 00:39:14,300
it must be him who did everything that happened today.

374
00:39:15,300 --> 00:39:17,300
He was the one who hurt Lady Pin.

375
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:18,300
But I don't think so

376
00:39:19,300 --> 00:39:23,300
because when I went to help Pin, I saw that Jiu was helping them both as well.

377
00:39:25,300 --> 00:39:27,300
He might act normal after attacking her.

378
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:29,300
Didn't you hear that he was Mr. Ma's subordinate?

379
00:39:35,300 --> 00:39:37,300
He must have been waiting for this opportunity for a long time.

380
00:39:38,300 --> 00:39:41,300
Jia, you called me to look at something in the room.

381
00:39:41,900 --> 00:39:42,400
What did you see?

382
00:39:47,300 --> 00:39:49,300
I saw Lady Pin and Mr. Tian,

383
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:52,300
and a stranger in that room.

384
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:55,300
So I thought he was a thief, so I called everyone to help.

385
00:39:56,300 --> 00:39:58,300
I doubted it was Jiu.

386
00:40:00,300 --> 00:40:02,300
Wow, you're still able to frame others shamelessly.

387
00:40:03,300 --> 00:40:04,300
It's the plan of yours and Madam Li.

388
00:40:06,300 --> 00:40:09,300
You are suspicious since Dong's funeral, Chan.

389
00:40:10,300 --> 00:40:11,300
And if Jiu is Mr. Ma's subordinate,

390
00:40:12,300 --> 00:40:15,300
it's your plan today.

391
00:40:16,300 --> 00:40:18,300
Then explain

392
00:40:18,700 --> 00:40:21,300
why did you keep all the workers out of the main building?

393
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:23,300
Yang already told you just now

394
00:40:24,300 --> 00:40:26,300
that Tian was also dizzy as well.

395
00:40:26,600 --> 00:40:28,300
Do you think that I would hurt my son?

396
00:40:29,300 --> 00:40:30,300
My son is gone.

397
00:40:31,300 --> 00:40:32,300
Tian. / Madam.

398
00:40:32,800 --> 00:40:33,300
Madam.

399
00:40:35,300 --> 00:40:38,300
Jia, take Li to rest.

400
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:40,300
Yes, Sir. Let's go.

401
00:40:49,300 --> 00:40:50,300
Ma.

402
00:40:51,300 --> 00:40:53,300
If you hurt my son,

403
00:40:54,300 --> 00:40:56,300
I won't let you get away.

404
00:42:01,300 --> 00:42:02,300
Madam.

405
00:42:05,300 --> 00:42:06,300
Jia.

406
00:42:07,300 --> 00:42:08,300
Madam.

407
00:42:09,300 --> 00:42:10,300
What happened?

408
00:42:11,300 --> 00:42:13,300
What did you see in that room?

409
00:42:14,300 --> 00:42:15,300
Wasn't Tian there?

410
00:42:22,300 --> 00:42:23,300
I saw…

411
00:42:24,300 --> 00:42:25,300
Tian.

412
00:42:34,300 --> 00:42:37,300
It must be because of the effect of the orchids that we gave him.

413
00:42:38,100 --> 00:42:39,300
When he met Jiu,

414
00:42:39,900 --> 00:42:40,400
so he...

415
00:42:44,300 --> 00:42:45,300
My Tian.

416
00:42:48,300 --> 00:42:50,300
I don't know what he will do to him.

417
00:42:52,300 --> 00:42:54,300
But now he knows my son's secret.

418
00:42:56,300 --> 00:42:58,300
We must hurry to find Jiu

419
00:42:58,800 --> 00:43:00,300
before he tells Mr. Ma the secret.

420
00:43:00,800 --> 00:43:02,300
Or else my son will be in big trouble.

421
00:43:04,300 --> 00:43:05,300
Yes, Madam.

422
00:43:35,300 --> 00:43:36,300
Tian.

423
00:43:44,300 --> 00:43:45,300
Tian, wait.

424
00:43:48,300 --> 00:43:50,300
How are you? Still have a headache?

425
00:43:53,300 --> 00:43:54,300
I'm fine.

426
00:43:54,700 --> 00:43:56,300
I can take care of myself.

427
00:43:58,300 --> 00:44:00,300
Please don't mess with me anymore.

428
00:44:02,300 --> 00:44:04,300
Hey, wait.

429
00:44:06,300 --> 00:44:08,300
Why are you saying this?

430
00:44:09,300 --> 00:44:12,300
You are not just someone else to me.

431
00:44:17,000 --> 00:44:19,300
I don't know...

432
00:44:21,000 --> 00:44:24,300
how it happened.

433
00:44:31,300 --> 00:44:33,300
I'm sorry.

434
00:44:36,000 --> 00:44:38,300
What happened

435
00:44:39,000 --> 00:44:41,300
was a mistake.

436
00:44:51,000 --> 00:44:53,300
A mistake?

437
00:45:00,000 --> 00:45:02,300
What about that you said you loved me?

438
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:08,300
You deceived me?

439
00:45:18,000 --> 00:45:20,300
I got it now.

440
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:25,000
You probably do this often.

441
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:27,600
I'm a fool for believing you.

442
00:45:27,600 --> 00:45:29,300
It's not like that.

443
00:45:32,300 --> 00:45:34,300
But it shouldn't happen.

444
00:45:36,300 --> 00:45:39,300
Because both of us are men.

445
00:45:39,300 --> 00:45:41,300
I know it shouldn't be.

446
00:45:43,300 --> 00:45:45,300
But I tried to restrain myself.

447
00:45:48,300 --> 00:45:50,300
I stopped you from coming to me.

448
00:45:50,300 --> 00:45:53,300
I was afraid that I couldn't to restrain myself.

449
00:45:54,300 --> 00:45:57,300
I've tried to suppress my feelings.

450
00:45:57,300 --> 00:45:59,300
But I couldn't do it.

451
00:46:03,300 --> 00:46:06,300
The more I suppress it, the more I feel.

452
00:46:08,300 --> 00:46:11,300
I want to protect you, Tian.

453
00:46:11,300 --> 00:46:15,300
I want to take care of you. I'm worried about you.

454
00:46:16,300 --> 00:46:22,300
I tried to force myself to stop all these feelings, but I couldn't.

455
00:46:23,300 --> 00:46:24,800
Jiu.

456
00:46:26,300 --> 00:46:29,300
But you call all these feelings a mistake?

457
00:46:33,300 --> 00:46:36,300
It's not love for you?

458
00:46:46,300 --> 00:46:48,300
All that time,

459
00:46:51,300 --> 00:46:53,300
I thought that...

460
00:46:54,300 --> 00:46:57,300
it was just me who have feelings for you.

461
00:47:02,300 --> 00:47:04,300
I'm not dreaming, right?

462
00:47:11,300 --> 00:47:13,300
You're not dreaming.

463
00:47:14,300 --> 00:47:16,300
I won't leave you.

464
00:47:18,300 --> 00:47:21,300
I will take care of you.

465
00:47:21,300 --> 00:47:23,300
I promise.

466
00:48:06,300 --> 00:48:09,300
Li let all the workers work at the back of the farm.

467
00:48:10,000 --> 00:48:12,300
You and your mother were locked away. Pin was attacked

468
00:48:13,300 --> 00:48:15,300
Tian disappeared along with Jiu.

469
00:48:15,300 --> 00:48:19,300
Do you want me to believe that Jiu did these alone?

470
00:48:19,600 --> 00:48:20,300
What do you mean?

471
00:48:22,300 --> 00:48:26,300
Are you sure that your mother didn't lure you into the barn together?

472
00:48:27,300 --> 00:48:29,300
Do you mean that you doubt Mother?

473
00:48:29,800 --> 00:48:31,300
Jiu is Ma's subordinate.

474
00:48:32,300 --> 00:48:34,300
Last time, Ma interfered with Dong's funeral.

475
00:48:35,300 --> 00:48:37,300
I'm still suspicious of your mother.

476
00:48:37,300 --> 00:48:39,600
But when I was trapped in the barn, Mother was there as well.

477
00:48:39,600 --> 00:48:41,300
So how can you be sure...

478
00:48:41,300 --> 00:48:43,300
that she and Jiu didn't know about this?

479
00:48:44,300 --> 00:48:48,300
But the one who ordered all the workers out of the house was Madam Li.

480
00:48:51,300 --> 00:48:53,300
Why didn't Jiu stay with all the workers?

481
00:48:56,300 --> 00:48:59,300
He must have been waiting for this opportunity for a long time.

482
00:48:59,300 --> 00:49:02,300
But don't tell me that Chan is involved in this.

483
00:49:03,300 --> 00:49:05,300
I definitely won't let her get away.

484
00:49:17,300 --> 00:49:18,700
Can't you knock on the door?

485
00:49:18,700 --> 00:49:20,300
Where is my son? Tell me.

486
00:49:25,300 --> 00:49:26,300
No idea.

487
00:49:27,000 --> 00:49:29,300
But even if I know, I won't tell you.

488
00:49:31,300 --> 00:49:34,300
Nuan, look at the sinner's face

489
00:49:35,300 --> 00:49:36,300
and remember it as a lesson.

490
00:49:37,300 --> 00:49:42,300
Don't go bad, otherwise Karma will go after your child instead.

491
00:49:42,800 --> 00:49:43,300
Yes, Madam.

492
00:49:46,300 --> 00:49:48,300
Don't look at me. Look at the face of the wicked.

493
00:49:48,800 --> 00:49:49,300
Yes, Madam.

494
00:49:50,300 --> 00:49:53,300
Do you think your son will replace Tian easily?

495
00:49:54,300 --> 00:49:57,300
You work with Mr. Ma in the hopes of overthrowing Tian.

496
00:49:58,300 --> 00:50:00,300
What do you exchange for? What did you use to lure him?

497
00:50:03,300 --> 00:50:05,300
You caused the trouble yourself, but blamed others.

498
00:50:06,300 --> 00:50:09,300
Tian's wedding is about to get cancelled.

499
00:50:10,300 --> 00:50:12,300
His succession has to be postponed.

500
00:50:13,300 --> 00:50:16,300
I don't see the need to find a way to overthrow him.

501
00:50:18,300 --> 00:50:19,300
It's you

502
00:50:20,300 --> 00:50:23,300
who waste your energy to plan to do evil things.

503
00:50:24,300 --> 00:50:25,300
I'll tell you something.

504
00:50:26,300 --> 00:50:27,300
All the chaos that happened

505
00:50:28,300 --> 00:50:31,300
resulted from the fact that you wanted to protect Tian.

506
00:50:32,300 --> 00:50:35,300
If anything happened to my son, I won't let you get away for sure.

507
00:50:36,300 --> 00:50:39,300
Take the time threatening me to find your son.

508
00:50:39,300 --> 00:50:41,500
He might have already been killed by this time.

509
00:50:41,500 --> 00:50:43,300
Madam Chan.

510
00:50:44,300 --> 00:50:46,300
I said this out of concern.

511
00:50:46,300 --> 00:50:47,300
Not a curse.

512
00:51:18,300 --> 00:51:19,300
Tian.

513
00:51:21,300 --> 00:51:22,800
Why are you outside?

514
00:51:22,800 --> 00:51:24,300
Aren't you cold?

515
00:51:27,300 --> 00:51:30,300
We disappear like this.

516
00:51:32,300 --> 00:51:35,300
I don't know what they are like now at home.

517
00:51:35,300 --> 00:51:37,300
It must be a big mess.

518
00:51:39,300 --> 00:51:41,300
So shall we go back?

519
00:51:41,300 --> 00:51:42,600
No.

520
00:51:42,600 --> 00:51:44,300
We can't go back.

521
00:51:44,300 --> 00:51:47,300
Mother saw me and you sleeping together.

522
00:51:47,300 --> 00:51:49,300
If we go back,

523
00:51:50,300 --> 00:51:53,300
I don't know what you will get.

524
00:51:56,300 --> 00:51:58,300
Don't worry about that.

525
00:51:58,300 --> 00:52:01,000
I can protect myself.

526
00:52:01,000 --> 00:52:03,300
No one can hurt me.

527
00:52:03,300 --> 00:52:05,300
Jiu.

528
00:52:07,300 --> 00:52:10,300
You don't know my mother well enough.

529
00:52:10,300 --> 00:52:13,300
She wants me to inherit the title.

530
00:52:13,300 --> 00:52:17,300
Her big deal is the Five Dragons Association.

531
00:52:17,300 --> 00:52:19,300
And she...

532
00:52:38,300 --> 00:52:40,300
My mother killed a man.

533
00:52:41,300 --> 00:52:45,300
She needs to hide the secret that I'm a homosexual.

534
00:52:45,300 --> 00:52:48,300
And she saw you with me.

535
00:52:49,300 --> 00:52:53,300
If we go back, she won't let you go for sure.

536
00:52:55,300 --> 00:52:57,300
So this is your secret?

537
00:53:01,300 --> 00:53:05,300
And how does it affect the assumption of your position?

538
00:53:08,300 --> 00:53:11,300
I like a man.

539
00:53:13,300 --> 00:53:16,300
I can't take the position.

540
00:53:16,300 --> 00:53:18,300
Why?

541
00:53:18,300 --> 00:53:20,800
Even though you're doing your job well,

542
00:53:20,800 --> 00:53:23,300
and loved by everyone?

543
00:53:28,300 --> 00:53:32,300
Yes, my father would definitely not accept it.

544
00:53:35,300 --> 00:53:37,300
In the past,

545
00:53:38,300 --> 00:53:41,300
there was a member of the association that was like me.

546
00:53:43,300 --> 00:53:46,300
Then he was oppressed until he had to commit suicide.

547
00:53:49,300 --> 00:53:52,300
So my mother had to keep a secret

548
00:53:53,300 --> 00:53:56,300
that I like men.

549
00:54:07,300 --> 00:54:09,300
If everyone knows,

550
00:54:11,300 --> 00:54:14,300
the Song family will be ruined because of me.

551
00:54:16,300 --> 00:54:19,300
I don't want to be the head of the association.

552
00:54:21,300 --> 00:54:22,300
I never wanted to.

553
00:54:26,300 --> 00:54:28,300
I just want to be me.

554
00:55:09,300 --> 00:55:11,300
About that day?

555
00:55:12,300 --> 00:55:15,300
Actually, it's weird.

556
00:55:16,300 --> 00:55:20,300
That day, Aunt Li urged me and Tian to drink tea.

557
00:55:21,300 --> 00:55:23,300
Then Tian was sick.

558
00:55:24,300 --> 00:55:27,300
Or was he sick because of that cup of tea?

559
00:55:28,300 --> 00:55:30,300
But why would Aunt Li poison Tian?

560
00:55:32,300 --> 00:55:34,300
This is what I suspect.

561
00:55:34,800 --> 00:55:37,300
Because it seemed like she let Jiu catch Tian.

562
00:55:42,300 --> 00:55:43,300
Yang.

563
00:55:45,300 --> 00:55:47,300
Did Jiu really capture Tian?

564
00:55:48,300 --> 00:55:52,300
Pin, he's Mr. Ma's subordinate.

565
00:55:52,800 --> 00:55:56,300
They both disappeared like this, how can I think in another way?

566
00:56:00,300 --> 00:56:01,300
Let's go.

567
00:56:01,500 --> 00:56:02,300
Yes.

568
00:56:04,300 --> 00:56:05,300
Let's go.

569
00:56:13,300 --> 00:56:17,300
But I don't think it was like that.

570
00:56:24,300 --> 00:56:27,300
Pin, you go back. I have some business.

571
00:56:27,800 --> 00:56:28,300
What's wrong?

572
00:56:29,300 --> 00:56:31,300
Just go back. I'll explain to you later.

573
00:56:32,300 --> 00:56:33,300
Yang.

574
00:56:43,300 --> 00:56:44,300
It hurts.

575
00:56:46,300 --> 00:56:48,300
Mei, how are you?

576
00:56:49,300 --> 00:56:52,300
Where is Jiu? Please help me.

577
00:56:53,300 --> 00:56:54,300
Mei.

578
00:56:55,300 --> 00:56:58,300
Wait a moment. I'll go get the medicine.

579
00:56:59,300 --> 00:57:00,300
It hurts.

580
00:57:01,300 --> 00:57:02,300
So bad.

581
00:57:04,300 --> 00:57:06,300
Jiu hasn't got anything yet, Sir?

582
00:57:07,300 --> 00:57:09,300
That girl can't even get up anymore.

583
00:57:09,600 --> 00:57:11,300
She sleeps all day and talks nonsense.

584
00:57:12,300 --> 00:57:14,300
I'm afraid that she will become addicted to opium to death.

585
00:57:14,900 --> 00:57:16,300
Dead? Is Mei dying?

586
00:57:18,300 --> 00:57:21,300
You poison her? You bastard, bastard.

587
00:57:22,300 --> 00:57:25,300
Let me go. Let go of me. Help.

588
00:57:25,600 --> 00:57:26,300
Annoying.

589
00:57:29,300 --> 00:57:32,300
Punk, don't be stubborn with me.

590
00:57:32,700 --> 00:57:33,300
Or you'll die.

591
00:57:39,300 --> 00:57:41,300
Gui, lock him up.

592
00:57:42,300 --> 00:57:43,300
Yes, Sir.

593
00:57:44,300 --> 00:57:45,300
Go.

594
00:57:47,300 --> 00:57:49,300
Bastard, evil.

595
00:57:49,800 --> 00:57:52,300
Let me go, bastard. Let me go.

596
00:57:53,300 --> 00:57:54,300
Evil.

597
00:57:56,300 --> 00:57:57,300
Mei.

598
00:57:58,300 --> 00:58:02,300
Hey, tie him tight. Find something to cover his mouth.

599
00:58:02,800 --> 00:58:03,300
Don't let him make any noise.

600
00:58:05,300 --> 00:58:06,300
Bastard.

601
00:58:08,300 --> 00:58:11,300
Put it in his mouth. Right.

602
00:58:12,300 --> 00:58:13,300
Be quiet.

603
00:58:16,300 --> 00:58:18,300
You're lucky that I didn't kill you.

604
00:58:18,800 --> 00:58:20,300
Wait for me here and don't even think about running away.

605
00:58:24,300 --> 00:58:26,300
Sir, Madam Chan is here.

606
00:58:37,300 --> 00:58:40,300
Madam, please come inside.

607
00:58:45,300 --> 00:58:46,300
She really comes here.

608
00:58:48,300 --> 00:58:50,300
That's your mother, right?

609
00:58:51,300 --> 00:58:52,300
Yes, it's my mom.

610
00:58:54,300 --> 00:58:55,300
Pin.

611
00:58:57,300 --> 00:58:58,300
Why did you follow me?

612
00:58:58,700 --> 00:59:00,300
I told you to go back. It's dangerous.

613
00:59:01,300 --> 00:59:03,300
Because of this, I have to follow you.

614
00:59:04,300 --> 00:59:07,300
I can't just sit still and let you risk your life alone.

615
00:59:25,300 --> 00:59:27,300
What is this about?

616
00:59:28,300 --> 00:59:30,300
Why do we spy on them?

617
00:59:31,300 --> 00:59:32,300
And who do your mother meet?

618
00:59:36,300 --> 00:59:40,300
Mr. Song already knew that Jiu was your subordinate.

619
00:59:41,300 --> 00:59:42,300
Who told him?

620
00:59:43,300 --> 00:59:44,300
Cai Xiaotong.

621
00:59:45,300 --> 00:59:48,300
Xiaotong, bitch.

622
00:59:49,300 --> 00:59:52,300
How dare she told big brother about me.

623
00:59:52,700 --> 00:59:56,300
If I am in trouble, I'll kill her.

624
01:00:00,300 --> 01:00:04,300
What did he say after knowing that Jiu is my subordinate?

625
01:00:05,300 --> 01:00:06,300
He let people look for him.

626
01:00:07,300 --> 01:00:09,300
I think that Jiu caught Tian and escaped.

627
01:00:11,300 --> 01:00:12,300
And didn't he come here?

628
01:00:13,300 --> 01:00:14,300
No.

629
01:00:15,300 --> 01:00:16,300
So did he send you any news?

630
01:00:22,300 --> 01:00:24,300
You must hurry and find him no matter what.

631
01:00:25,300 --> 01:00:29,300
Or it's better to make him and Tian disappear forever.

632
01:00:31,300 --> 01:00:32,300
And don't forget.

633
01:00:33,300 --> 01:00:35,300
Don't ever say that I was part of it.

634
01:00:44,300 --> 01:00:45,300
That is…

635
01:00:50,300 --> 01:00:52,300
Pin, listen to me.

636
01:00:52,600 --> 01:00:54,300
You go back. I'll tell you later.

637
01:00:55,300 --> 01:00:56,300
Please, I'm begging you.

638
01:00:57,300 --> 01:00:58,300
Go back.

639
01:00:59,300 --> 01:01:00,300
Okay.

640
01:01:16,300 --> 01:01:17,300
Mom!

641
01:01:18,300 --> 01:01:20,300
Yang, how did you get here?

642
01:01:21,300 --> 01:01:22,300
It's not what you think.

643
01:01:22,800 --> 01:01:23,300
Don't say anything.

644
01:01:24,300 --> 01:01:25,300
Listen to me first.

645
01:01:25,600 --> 01:01:26,300
No need to explain now. Run first.

646
01:01:27,300 --> 01:01:28,300
Run? Why?

647
01:01:28,700 --> 01:01:29,300
Father is here.

648
01:01:29,600 --> 01:01:30,300
Huh?

649
01:01:34,300 --> 01:01:36,300
You can't come in, Sir.

650
01:01:43,300 --> 01:01:44,300
Are you sure?

651
01:02:11,300 --> 01:02:12,300
Big Brother.

652
01:02:22,300 --> 01:02:23,300
This way, please.

653
01:02:25,300 --> 01:02:27,300
Get out from the back so no one sees you.

654
01:02:28,300 --> 01:02:29,300
Go straight a bit and you've reached the exit.

655
01:02:30,300 --> 01:02:33,300
I need to go back to Mr. Ma. Please excuse me.

656
01:02:35,300 --> 01:02:36,300
Yang.

657
01:02:36,600 --> 01:02:37,300
Don't say anything.

658
01:02:38,300 --> 01:02:40,300
When we get home, we have a lot to discuss.

659
01:02:42,300 --> 01:02:43,300
Let's go, Madam.

660
01:03:19,300 --> 01:03:21,300
What happened? Why are you tied like this?

661
01:03:22,300 --> 01:03:24,300
Brother, help me and my sister please.

662
01:03:51,300 --> 01:03:52,300
Hey.

663
01:03:52,500 --> 01:03:53,300
Hey.

664
01:03:54,300 --> 01:03:57,300
Brother, please get us out of here.

665
01:04:07,300 --> 01:04:08,300
Tea, big brother.

666
01:04:44,300 --> 01:04:45,300
Follow me.

667
01:05:12,300 --> 01:05:14,300
They're there. Hold them.

668
01:05:14,300 --> 01:05:15,300
Go.

669
01:05:15,600 --> 01:05:16,300
Go.

670
01:05:17,300 --> 01:05:18,300
Stop.

671
01:05:20,300 --> 01:05:21,300
Where are you going?

672
01:05:24,300 --> 01:05:25,300
Go, go.

673
01:05:27,300 --> 01:05:28,300
Hey.

674
01:05:28,600 --> 01:05:31,300
Please take Mei with you. Don't worry about me.

675
01:06:10,300 --> 01:06:11,300
Hey, check over there.

676
01:06:22,300 --> 01:06:23,300
Help me, help.

677
01:06:24,300 --> 01:06:26,300
A culprit caught a child and went over there.

678
01:06:26,600 --> 01:06:27,300
He also snatched my bag.

679
01:06:27,700 --> 01:06:28,300
Let's go.

680
01:06:46,300 --> 01:06:47,300
I told you already

681
01:06:48,300 --> 01:06:50,300
that I didn't know anything.

682
01:06:50,600 --> 01:06:51,300
How did you not know?

683
01:06:52,300 --> 01:06:54,300
I know that Jiu is your subordinate.

684
01:06:55,300 --> 01:06:57,300
You sent him to hurt my son.

685
01:06:58,300 --> 01:06:59,300
Where is my son now? Tell me.

686
01:07:01,300 --> 01:07:04,300
If you want to accuse us, you should at least have a proof, Sir.

687
01:07:05,300 --> 01:07:06,300
Shut up!

688
01:07:26,300 --> 01:07:27,300
Ma.

689
01:07:29,300 --> 01:07:31,300
In the past, you have caused a lot of troubles.

690
01:07:32,300 --> 01:07:33,300
I tried to be patient

691
01:07:35,300 --> 01:07:38,300
for the sake of our brotherhood and friendship.

692
01:07:39,300 --> 01:07:41,300
But this time, I can't stand it.

693
01:07:42,300 --> 01:07:44,300
because you hurt my child.

694
01:07:45,300 --> 01:07:46,300
Ma.

695
01:07:51,300 --> 01:07:53,300
You know me best.

696
01:07:55,300 --> 01:07:57,300
You know what kind of person I was in the past.

697
01:07:58,300 --> 01:08:03,300
Don't force me to become a cruel man like before.

698
01:08:13,300 --> 01:08:14,300
I told you already

699
01:08:16,300 --> 01:08:19,300
that I didn't know where Tian is.

700
01:08:20,300 --> 01:08:21,300
Then remember well.

701
01:08:24,300 --> 01:08:25,300
If anything happened to Tian,

702
01:08:28,300 --> 01:08:30,300
I'll kill you.

703
01:09:21,300 --> 01:09:23,300
Have you ever seen two men in this picture?

704
01:09:23,600 --> 01:09:25,300
I don't know where he takes Mr. Tian to?

705
01:09:25,800 --> 01:09:28,300
We have to Kill Jiu to let Tian's secret die with him.

706
01:09:30,300 --> 01:09:33,300
If one day I do something bad to you,

707
01:09:33,600 --> 01:09:34,300
can you forgive me?

708
01:09:35,300 --> 01:09:38,300
If they are woman and man, I think that they have eloped.

709
01:09:39,300 --> 01:09:40,300
Where is beetle orchid?

710
01:09:44,300 --> 01:09:45,300
Jia, Jia.

711
01:09:46,300 --> 01:09:49,300
We got the news about Jiu's hiding place, Sir.

712
01:09:53,300 --> 01:09:54,300
Jiu.

713
01:09:54,600 --> 01:09:55,300
Yang.
